<%= @user.first_name %>, 

Here is a list of your recent reservation activity. Please check it carefully. If there are any mistakes you can correct them on our web site or e-mail us at dan@thearmnyc.com.

<% if @current_reservations.size > 0 %> 
Your reservations: 

<% @current_reservations.each do |reservation| %>
<%= reservation.date.strftime("%m/%d/%Y") %> - <%= HOURS.index(reservation.hour) %> - <%= reservation.press.name %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

<% if @cancellations.size > 0 %>
Cancellations:
<% @cancellations.each do |reservation| %>
<%= reservation.date.strftime("%m/%d/%Y") %> - <%= HOURS.index(reservation.hour) %> - <%= reservation.press.name %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

